.description
Demo of AmigaCOMAL (missing only SAVE), an incremental p-code compiler from
Denmark.  COMAL is a language with the design goal of combining the modern
structured approach of Pascal with the ease of use and interactivity of
BASIC.  There are versions of COMAL for IBM, VAX, CP/M, C-64, Amiga and
various European operating systems.  Includes a complete turtle graphics
package.  Is perfect for education yet powerful enough for applications
programming.  
